    "media:imagetext": "TWA\nTIMETABLE\nEFFECTIVE FEBRUARY 1—FEBRUARY 28, 1981\nTWA unseats\nthe competition.\nTWA\nTWA's new Ambassador Classs™\nto Europe gives you more room\nthan any other airline.\nAvailable on every 747 to Europe by June, 1981:\n• New, wider seats, more leg room.\n• Pair seating so everyone is either by a window or\nan aisle.\n• Speedy, special Ambassador Class check-in.\nAdvance seat selection.\nRound-trip check-in.\nFree drinks and appetizers in-flight.\nWe take care of you so\nyou can take care of business.",
